data.description: Welcome to your new cozy and inviting ranch-style home, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a range of fantastic amenities. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Sliding glass doors leading to a spacious rear deck with a charming gazebo, perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Eye-catching brick front for timeless curb appeal. Stay warm and cozy with a wood-burning stove during the colder months. Enjoy privacy and security with a fenced rear yard.  Detached 2-car garage for convenient parking and additional storage.  Brand new furnace, air conditioning, and hot water heater for energy efficiency and peace of mind. This home offers the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living, making it an ideal space for you and your family. Whether you're looking to entertain friends on the deck, cozy up by the wood-burning stove.
